Q: How do I sign up for our Clubs & Societies?
A: During your inductions, a Clubs & Societies Sign-Up form will be shared. This is your way of showing your interest in any of our Clubs & Societies, who will follow up with you. All clubs and societies are free (there is no charge) to join. CLICK HERE TO VIEW CLUBS & SOCIETIES SIGN-UP FORM
